snippet.title: Tedd'or WoD (lvl. 10/11) Newcomer Gameplay
snippet.description:
Hope you like it! Playing low levels in WoD is hard because you have almost no gear. The lvl. 5/6 video has higher score because I didn't upgrade my gear enough for this lvl. 10/11.

WoD (Well of Depths) is a competitive gamemode in my game, Tedd'or.
https://jdev.com.es/teddor
